<plot>Forces collide in "Breaking News" between the big business of TV news and journalistic ethics. Watch in great detail how TV reporters scramble to report on every tawdry detail of the Michael Jackson and Kobe Bryant trials, trying to pass them off as news. "Breaking News" chronicles the vast resources the modern media corporations pour into these cases for ratings and dollars.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?082303</url></doc>
